-- Russia Seeks Adoption Agreement With U.S. by End of Year, Ombudsman Says
-- Lyubov Pronina
-- 2010-07-12T10:45:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/russia-seeks-adoption-agreement-with-u-s-by-end-of-year-ombudsman-says.html

          
          
             Russia hopes to conclude an
agreement with the U.S. on adoption by year-end, Pavel Astakhov,
Russia’s ombudsman for children’s rights, told reporters in
Moscow today.  
